<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RPL Integrator - API Gateway</title>
    <meta name="description" content="RPL Integrator adalah dashboard API Gateway untuk routing service, logging request, API key, analytics, tabel shadow, dan data karyawan.">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/kong-theme.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <style>
        .hero-container { width: min(100%, 1120px); padding: 68px 28px 36px; color: #fff; }
        .hero-top { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14); color: #bfdbfe; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .hero-title { max-width: 860px; font-size: 54px; line-height: 1.04; font-weight: 850; margin-bottom: 18px; }
        .hero-subtitle { max-width: 720px; font-size: 17px; color: #bfd0e2; margin-bottom: 34px; line-height: 1.7; }
        .action-buttons { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 14px; }
        .btn-outline-light { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.22); color: #fff; background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); }
        .btn-outline-light:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.14); color: #fff; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.32); }
        .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 16px; margin: 46px 0 0; }
        .feature-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.13); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 20px; backdrop-filter: blur(10px); transition: background .25s ease, border-color .25s ease, transform .25s ease; animation: fadeInUp .5s ease both; }
        .feature-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: .30s; } .feature-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: .38s; } .feature-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: .46s; } .feature-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: .54s; } .feature-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: .62s; } .feature-card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: .70s; }
        .feature-card:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.13); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.24); transform: translateY(-3px); }
        .feature-icon { width: 38px; height: 38px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 10px; color: #67e8f9; background: rgba(8,145,178,.18); margin-bottom: 14px; }
        .feature-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .feature-desc { font-size: 13px; color: #b6c7da; line-height: 1.55; }
        .stack-strip { margin-top: 44px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); animation: fadeInUp .5s ease .72s both; }
        .stack-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 800; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; margin-bottom: 14px; }
        .stack-list { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .stack-pill { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: #dbeafe; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); padding: 8px 14px; border-radius: 999px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); }
        .landing-footer { margin-top: 34px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; color: #94a3b8; font-size: 13px; }
        .landing-links { display: flex; gap: 16px; }
        .landing-links a { color: #93c5fd; text-decoration: none; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
        @media (max-width: 900px) { .hero-title { font-size: 40px; } .features-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); } }
        @media (max-width: 560px) { .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .hero-container { padding-top: 86px; } }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="no-sidebar">
    <div style="position:absolute;top:24px;right:24px;z-index:999"><button class="btn btn-outline" id="darkModeToggle" title="Ubah mode tampilan" style="border-radius:50%;padding:8px;width:38px;height:38px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><i data-lucide="moon"></i></button></div>
    <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="hero-top" style="animation: fadeInUp .5s ease both;"><i data-lucide="network"></i> RPL Integrator</div>
        <h1 class="hero-title" style="animation: fadeInUp .6s ease .08s both;">Satu pintu untuk memantau dan menguji integrasi service</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle" style="animation: fadeInUp .6s ease .16s both;">Dashboard API Gateway untuk mengatur routing, melihat log request, mengelola API key, membaca tabel shadow, dan menilai efektivitas penggunaan service dari aplikasi sumber.</p>

        <div class="action-buttons" style="animation: fadeInUp .6s ease .24s both;">
            <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary"><i data-lucide="log-in"></i> Masuk ke Dashboard</a>
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-outline-light"><i data-lucide="user-plus"></i> Daftar Akun</a>
            <a href="/api/status" class="btn btn-outline-light"><i data-lucide="activity"></i> Cek Status API</a>
        </div>

        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i data-lucide="route"></i></div><div class="feature-title">Routing Gateway</div><div class="feature-desc">Request diarahkan ke service tujuan berdasarkan konfigurasi database.</div></div>
            <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i data-lucide="clipboard-list"></i></div><div class="feature-title">Logging Request</div><div class="feature-desc">Aktivitas gateway tersimpan sebagai audit trail yang mudah diperiksa.</div></div>
            <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i data-lucide="key-round"></i></div><div class="feature-title">Kunci API</div><div class="feature-desc">Akses integrasi dapat dibatasi dengan API key dan kuota harian.</div></div>
            <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i data-lucide="bar-chart-3"></i></div><div class="feature-title">Analitik</div><div class="feature-desc">Traffic, tingkat sukses, dan konsumen teratas terlihat dalam grafik.</div></div>
            <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i data-lucide="database"></i></div><div class="feature-title">Tabel Shadow</div><div class="feature-desc">Penggunaan service dari aplikasi sumber dicatat tanpa mengganggu log utama.</div></div>
            <div class="feature-card"><div class="feature-icon"><i data-lucide="id-card"></i></div><div class="feature-title">Data Karyawan</div><div class="feature-desc">Data demo karyawan tersedia untuk bukti repository dan presentasi.</div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="stack-strip">
            <div class="stack-title">Teknologi proyek</div>
            <div class="stack-list">
                <span class="stack-pill"><i data-lucide="server" style="width:16px;height:16px"></i> Node.js</span>
                <span class="stack-pill"><i data-lucide="layers" style="width:16px;height:16px"></i> Express</span>
                <span class="stack-pill"><i data-lucide="database" style="width:16px;height:16px"></i> MySQL</span>
                <span class="stack-pill"><i data-lucide="layout-template" style="width:16px;height:16px"></i> EJS</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer class="landing-footer">
            <div>© 2026 Kelompok 7 - Tugas Besar RPL 2 ULBI</div>
            <div class="landing-links">
                <a href="/download-docs"><i data-lucide="file-text" style="width:14px;height:14px"></i> Dokumentasi</a>
                <a href="/api/status"><i data-lucide="activity" style="width:14px;height:14px"></i> Status</a>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            lucide.createIcons();
            const toggle = document.getElementById('darkModeToggle');
            if (!toggle) return;
            const isDark = localStorage.getItem('darkMode') === 'true';
            if (isDark) document.body.classList.add('dark-mode');
            toggle.innerHTML = isDark ? '<i data-lucide="sun"></i>' : '<i data-lucide="moon"></i>';
            lucide.createIcons();
            toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
                document.body.classList.toggle('dark-mode');
                const dark = document.body.classList.contains('dark-mode');
                localStorage.setItem('darkMode', dark);
                toggle.innerHTML = dark ? '<i data-lucide="sun"></i>' : '<i data-lucide="moon"></i>';
                lucide.createIcons();
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>
